\fs18 \cf4 \cb31 \strokec4 The corners of Orphie's room are filled with all sorts of cat supplies: a cat tree for climbing, a soft cushion, a scratching post that won't break, and carefully selected toys...\cb1 \
\cb31 "I'm always worried about finding a sick, homeless cat near the outpost... If I have these things ready in advance, it'll be easier for them to stay here..."\cb1 \
\cb31 "Though we can't keep cats in the camp... I'll definitely find a kind owner for them within the captain's deadline!"\cb1 \
\cb31 "But Orphie, those things have been in the dorm for three years, and you still haven't found such a cat!"\cb1 \
